Question: 1.  Do you like shopping?
Answer (EN)::
Yes, I like shopping.
I like buying new clothes.
Shopping is fun.
Javob (UZ)::
Ha, men xarid qilishni yoqtiraman.
Men yangi kiyimlar sotib olishni yaxshi ko‘raman.
Xarid qilish qiziqarli.

Question: 2.  Do you go shopping on Sundays?
Answer (EN)::
Yes, I go shopping on Sundays.
I go with my family.
We buy food and clothes.
Javob (UZ)::
Ha, men yakshanba kunlari xarid qilaman.
Men oilam bilan boraman.
Biz ovqat va kiyim olamiz.

Question: 3.  Do you buy your clothes online?
Answer (EN)::
Sometimes I buy clothes online.
It is easy and fast.
I like online shopping.
Javob (UZ)::
Ba’zan men kiyimlarni internetdan olaman.
Bu oson va tez.
Menga onlayn xarid yoqadi.

Question: 4.  Are clothes cheap in your country?
Answer (EN)::
Clothes are not very cheap in my country.
Some clothes are expensive.
I buy clothes on sale.
Javob (UZ)::
Mening mamlakatimda kiyimlar juda arzon emas.
Ba’zi kiyimlar qimmat.
Men chegirmada kiyim sotib olaman.

Question: 1.  How do you spend your free time?
Answer (EN):: I read books and cook food for my family.
Javob (UZ):: Men kitob o‘qiyman va oilam uchun ovqat pishiraman.

Question: 2.  How often do you go shopping?
Answer (EN)::
I go shopping once a week.
I buy food and clothes.
Javob (UZ)::
Men haftasiga bir marta xarid qilaman. 
Oziq-ovqat va kiyim sotib olaman.

Question: 3.  Speak about a shopping centre you like.
Answer (EN)::
I like “City Mall”. 
It is modern and comfortable.
I go there with my family.
Javob (UZ)::
Men “City Mall”ni yoqtiraman. 
U zamonaviy va qulay. 
Men oilam bilan boraman.

Question: 4.  Speak about your day.
Answer (EN)::
I wake up at 7 o’clock.
I go to work at 9 o’clock and come home at 8 p.m.
Javob (UZ)::
Men soat 7 da turaman. 
Men 9 da ishga boraman va 8 da uyga qaytaman.

Question: 1.  What is your hobby?
Answer (EN):: My hobbies are playing football and reading books.
Javob (UZ):: Mening hobbilarim futbol o‘ynash va kitob o‘qish.

Question: 2.  Do you like cooking at home?
Answer (EN)::
Yes, I like cooking.
I enjoy making plov.
Javob (UZ)::
Ha, men ovqat pishirishni yoqtiraman.
Plov qilishni yaxshi ko‘raman.

Question: 3.  Do you do morning exercises?
Answer (EN):: Yes, I do morning exercises every day.
Javob (UZ):: Ha, men har kuni ertalab mashq qilaman.

Question: 4.  Do you like watching films?
Answer (EN)::
Yes, I like watching films.
My favourite film is Prison Break.
Javob (UZ)::
Ha, men film tomosha qilishni yoqtiraman.
Mening sevimli filmim Prison Break.

Question: 1.  Speak about your last holiday.
Answer (EN)::
I went on holiday in July 2025.
I rested in the mountains.
Javob (UZ)::
Men 2025-yil iyul oyida ta’tilga chiqdim.
Tog‘da dam oldim.

Question: 2.  Speak about your last birthday party.
Answer (EN)::
I celebrated my birthday at home.
My family was with me.
Javob (UZ)::
Men tug‘ilgan kunimni uyda nishonladim.
Oilam yonimda edi.

Question: 3.  Speak about your house.
Answer (EN)::
My house is small but comfortable.
I live with my family.
Javob (UZ)::
Mening uyim kichik, lekin qulay. 
Men oilam bilan yashayman.

Question: 4.  Talk about a book you like.
Answer (EN)::
I like reading books.
My favourite book is Rich Dad Poor Dad.
I read it three times.
Javob (UZ)::
Men kitob o‘qishni yoqtiraman.
Sevimli kitobim Rich Dad Poor Dad.
Men uni uch marta o‘qiganman.

Question: 1.  Do you often get up early?
Answer (EN)::
Yes, I do.
I get up at 7 every day.
Javob (UZ)::
Ha, turaman. 
Men har kuni soat 7 da turaman.

Question: 2.  Do you always have breakfast with your family?
UZ tarjima:: Siz doimo oilangiz bilan nonushta qilasizmi?
Answer (EN):: Yes, I do. I always have breakfast with my family.
Javob (UZ)::
Ha, qilaman.
Men doimo oilam bilan nonushta qilaman.

Question: 3.  What time do you go to school / university / work?
UZ tarjima:: Siz maktabga / universitetga / ishga soat nechada borasiz?
Answer (EN):: I go to work at 8.
Javob (UZ):: Men ishga soat 8 da boraman.

Question: 4.  What time do you have dinner?
UZ tarjima:: Siz kechki ovqatni soat nechada yeysiz?
Answer (EN):: I do not have dinner.
Javob (UZ):: Men kechki ovqat yemayman.

Question: 1.  What do you do on Saturdays and Sundays?
UZ tarjima:: Shanba va yakshanba kunlari nima qilasiz?
Answer (EN):: I read books and cook food for my family.
Javob (UZ):: Men kitob o‘qiyman va oilam uchun ovqat pishiraman.

Question: 2.  Speak about the day of the week you do not like.
UZ tarjima:: Siz yoqtirmaydigan hafta kuni haqida gapiring.
Answer (EN):: I do not like Monday. I do not know why, but it is a hard day.
Javob (UZ):: Menga dushanba kuni yoqmaydi. Nima uchunligini bilmayman, lekin u og‘ir o‘tadi.

Question: 3.  Which days of the week do you have your English lessons?
UZ tarjima:: Siz ingliz tili darslarini haftaning qaysi kunlari o‘tasiz?
Answer (EN):: I have English lessons on Tuesday, Thursday, and Saturday at 6:30 p.m.
Javob (UZ):: Men ingliz tili darslarini seshanba, payshanba va shanba kunlari soat 6:30 da o‘qiyman.

Question: 4.  How often do you meet your friends? What do you do with them?
UZ tarjima:: Do‘stlaringiz bilan qanchalik tez-tez uchrashasiz? Ular bilan nima qilasiz?
Answer (EN)::
I meet my friends once a month. 
We remember our childhood.
Javob (UZ)::
Men do‘stlarim bilan oyda bir marta uchrashaman.
Ular bilan yoshlikni eslaymiz.

Question: 1.  Do you live in a house or flat?
Answer (EN):: I live in a house.
Javob (UZ):: Men uyda yashayman.

Question: 2.  How many rooms are there in your house/flat?
Answer (EN):: There are five bedrooms, two living rooms, two bathrooms, one toilet, and one kitchen.
Javob (UZ):: Mening uymda 5 ta yotoq xonasi, 2 ta mehmonxona, 2 ta hammom, 1 ta hojatxona va 1 ta oshxona bor.

Question: 3.  Which room do you like?
Answer (EN):: I like my own room.
Javob (UZ):: Men o‘zimning xonamni yoqtiraman.

Question: 4.  Why do you like this room?
UZ tarjima:: Nima uchun bu xona sizga yoqadi?
Answer (EN):: I like it because it is quiet and comfortable.
Javob (UZ):: Men uni yoqtiraman, chunki u tinch va qulay.

Question: 1.  What facilities are there in your house/flat?
Answer (EN)::
My house has free internet and an air conditioner. 
We have a beautiful garden.
Javob (UZ)::
Mening uyimda tekin internet va konditsioner bor.
Chiroyli bog‘imiz ham bor.

Question: 2.  Can you speak about your living room?
Answer (EN)::
My living room is big and comfortable. 
There is a sofa, a table, and a TV.
Javob (UZ):: Mening mehmonxonam katta va qulay. Unda divan, stol va televizor bor.

Question: 3.  Would you like to move house? Why?
Answer (EN)::
No, I do not want to move.
I like my house.
Javob (UZ)::
Yo‘q, men uyni almashtirmoqchi emasman.
Menga uyim yoqadi.

Question: 4.  What are expensive possessions in the house for you? Why?
UZ tarjima:: Uyingizdagi siz uchun qimmat buyumlar nima? Nima uchun?
Answer (EN):: My TV and computer are expensive for me because I use them every day.
Javob (UZ):: Mening televizor va kompyuterim qimmat, chunki men ularni har kuni ishlataman.
